name: Celestial Storm Booster Box

• There are 36 packs per display.

name: Celestial Storm Elite Trainer Box
extCardText:
Nature's Wrath in Full Fury!

Watch out for the vortex! It's a season of furious emerald storms and a sky alive with portents, as Pokemon and creatures from Ultra Space clash. Some ride the storm, and others defy it, with a lineup including Articuno-GX, Blaziken-GX, Scizor-GX, Stakataka-GX, and the amazing Rayquaza-GX, plus new cards featuring Latios, Latias, and Jirachi. Face the winds of change head-on in the Pokemon TCG: Sun & Moon - Celestial Storm!

Contents:
• 8 Celestial Storm booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Rayquaza
• 45 Energy cards
• A player's guide
• 6 damage-counter dice
• Competition-legal coin-flip die
• 2 acrylic condition markers
• 1 acrylic GX marker
• A collector's box
• 4 dividers
• A Pokemon Trading Card Game Online code card

name: Battle Arena Deck [Mega Charizard X]
cleanName: Battle Arena Deck Mega Charizard X
extCardText:
Mighty Mega Charizard X Battles for Victory!

Mega Charizard X is ready to heat up the battlefield in the new Pokémon TCG: Battle Arena Deck! This 60-card deck is ready to play right away, with powerful cards and winning strategies worthy of an ace Trainer. Each deck is led by an exceptional Mega Evolution Pokémon-EX and includes 11 foil cards. Let the battle begin!

In this 60-card deck, you'll find:
• 1 foil card featuring Mega Charizard-EX
• 1 foil card featuring Charizard-EX
• 8 foil basic Fire Energy cards
Tournament-level Trainer cards, including Brigette, Lysandre, Ultra Ball, and more!
In addition, each box contains:
• 1 metallic coin
• 2-player playmat and rulesheet
• 1 code card to play this deck online
• 1 deck box
• Damage counters
• 1 Quick Guide to unlock the powerful strategies within
(Coin may vary by product.)
